{"tid":504821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Ian McKellen（磁力王）：Actresses Used To Proposition Directors For Sex","createTime":"2017-12-20T12:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T04:43:14.000Z","uid":48083,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a1dbf9524006a484e1ed45f345781b4364d421c1","tid":504821,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T12:32:46.000Z","msg":"British actor Ian McKellen, condemning rampant sexual misconduct in show business, <strong>recalled a time when some actresses &ldquo;proposed that they should be a victim.&rdquo;</strong><br />\n<br />\nMcKellen, star of &ldquo;Lord of the Rings&rdquo; and &ldquo;X-Men,&rdquo; said during a recent appearance at Oxford Union that <strong>when he started his career in the early 1960s, some women applied for theater jobs with photographs marked with a special message to the directors.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The director of the theater I was working at showed me some photographs he got from women who were wanting jobs,&rdquo; he said. <span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;They were actors. And some of them had ― I think these were the initials ― at the bottom of their photograph &lsquo;DRR&rsquo; &mdash; directors&rsquo; rights respected.</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>&ldquo;In other words, &lsquo;If you give me a job, you can have sex with me.&rsquo; That was commonplace for people who proposed that they should be a victim. Madness.&rdquo;</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nMcKellen, who is gay, called Kevin Spacey&rsquo;s coming-out in response to misconduct allegations &ldquo;reprehensible.&rdquo; He expressed hope that predatory behavior could be &ldquo;eradicated.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I assume nothing but good will come out of these revelations, even though some people of course get wrongly accused &mdash; there&rsquo;s that side of it as well,&rdquo; he said.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/203220_c9349e0d2dbbee07a3ff7dfb74267fea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F203220_c9349e0d2dbbee07a3ff7dfb74267fea.jpg&h=d278812b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.huffpost.com/us/entry/us_5a38ea02e4b0c65287ac068f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.huffpost.com%2Fus%2Fentry%2Fus_5a38ea02e4b0c65287ac068f&d=L%2FuTO2Xyn%2BKc934WAUEEI8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=12a128fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.huffpost.com/us/entry/us_5a38ea02e4b0c65287ac068f</a>"},{"pid":"51ec8a8c5fd5d178499d090c118ab8e35a5bf83f","tid":504821,"uid":149494,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T12:50:42.000Z","msg":"一方面利用自己身體搵著數<br />\n另一方面又可以利用呢樣野作為武器反咬你一口<br />\n女人真係好屈<br />\n男人要唔咸濕先能夠生存到"},{"pid":"51117f1eeaa153448784e29a39b461034b3ad51e","tid":504821,"uid":26752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T13:05:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>女權西：呢d係女身自主</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17852e1fd28a799ac09c1f8237f71959b9d94c32","tid":504821,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T13:10:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一方面利用自己身體搵著數<br />\n另一方面又可以利用呢樣野作為武器反咬你一口<br />\n女人真係好屈<br />\n男人要唔咸濕先能夠生存到</blockquote><br />\n男人要切j或者做女人奴隸先生存到"},{"pid":"cd0d9d3bd613640cb6f96d675c66d50602f51d3a","tid":504821,"uid":123264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T13:11:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一方面利用自己身體搵著數<br />\n另一方面又可以利用呢樣野作為武器反咬你一口<br />\n女人真係好屈<br />\n男人要唔咸濕先能夠生存到</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">樣衰既</span>男人要切j或者做女人奴隸先生存到</blockquote>"},{"pid":"95c62677a913cb3ea3fa468e2669aa1463f4cf2d","tid":504821,"uid":118120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T13:14:52.000Z","msg":"用呂姓運動員一樣<br />\n有好處果時就痴去身邊男人, 到人地